H3.text: In which Yorkshire town is the Harlow Carr RHS Gardens situated. HARROGATE

A4.text: The garden is located on the western edge of Harrogate in North Yorkshire

A5.text: The garden is situated on Crag Lane, off Otley Road (B6162) about a mile and a half from the centre of Harrogate
